article_title: Former party chairman to seek Senate seat
article_text:
CH Online Access for Current Subscribers

Already have a subscription to the Chaska Herald that you sent in a check via US Mail or paid by cash/credit card? Activate your online account by using this option. Your email address and phone number you provided on your subscription form needs to match the same information your online user account. If you are having trouble or want to confirm what email address and phone number we have on your subscription account, call us at 952-345-6682 so we can help.

og.description: Scott Jensen, a former local chairman of the Republican Party and former school board member in Waconia School District, has announced his intention to seek the Republican nomination for Senate District 47 in 2016.
